-- Hooded Gunmen Shoot Mexican Mayor-Elect Four Times, El Universal Reports
-- B y   J o n a t h a n   R o e d e r
-- 2010-09-24T21:10:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-24/hooded-gunmen-shoot-mexican-mayor-elect-four-times-el-universal-reports.html
A mayor-elect in the Mexican state
of Chihuahua was seriously injured after being shot four times
by gunmen, Mexico City daily El Universal reported on its
website.  Ricardo Solis Manriquez, mayor-elect of the municipality of
Gran Morelos, was attacked by three hooded men with assault
rifles in his business, the daily said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jonathan Roeder in Mexico City at 
 jroeder@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jonathan Roeder at 
 jroeder@bloomberg.net  